{"tid":846358,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港島一日3宗爆竊案　山頂洋屋被抬走夾萬","createTime":"2018-10-03T10:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T12:10:48.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c03bc0f207a4c4fed09f185ecb37ef203bb3802","tid":846358,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"繼昨晚(2日)跑馬地及今早(3日)大潭陽明山莊發生爆竊案後，中午12時04分，山頂和福道14號一個洋房屋苑，又再發生爆竊案，其中一幢洋房的56歲外籍女戶主，發現兒子睡房的窗門撬開，內裏的夾萬及兩隻約值4萬2千港元戒指不翼而飛，相信遭賊人入屋爆竊，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，案件列作爆竊，大批警員在附近山頭搜捕賊蹤，但未有發現。據悉，戶主兒子正身處外地，警方在附近山坡尋回夾萬，但被搜掠一空，夾萬內有首飾、人民幣現金及手錶等。案件列爆竊，交由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n港島區在過去不足24小時內先後發生3宗爆竊案，警方高度關注案件，正調查是否同一幫賊匪所為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181003/bkn-20181003123715888-1003_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181003%2Fbkn-20181003123715888-1003_00822_001.html&d=8sSJMwHtD4KL2qumG5YIRjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=83841780\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181003/bkn-20181003123715888-1003_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f2b72ad26cabdf871c636e06ec7f731902f5f03d","tid":846358,"uid":53672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"國慶黃金週。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273c5ef29a138d01ec0ab5d81e8cf39dfa3c3a06","tid":846358,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"支蝻專才"},{"pid":"de8e85a2a3d083e8337c89bd8aa2b8c5e61fdcf1","tid":846358,"uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f2b72ad26cabdf871c636e06ec7f731902f5f03d","tid":846358,"uid":53672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"國慶黃金週。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/photowars/1387786809-1027422299.jpg\" data-th